1. *Mnogim* ljudima nedostaje druženje. (Many people miss socializing.)
2. Njihova priča inspiriše *mnoge*. (Their story inspires many.)
3. Ova knjiga je *mnogima* pomogla u životu. (This book helped many people in their life.)
4. *Mnogim* je učenicima matematika teška. (Math is difficult for many students.)
5. *Mnogim* turistima se svidela hrana u Srbiji. (Many tourists liked the food in Serbia.)
6. On ima *mnogo* novca. (He has a lot of money.)
7. *Mnogo* je važno redovno vežbati. (It's very important to exercise regularly.)
8. Ova situacija je *mnogo* teška za nas. (This situation is very difficult for us.)
9. Uzela sam *mnogo* knjiga iz biblioteke. (I took many books from the library.)
10. Oni *mnogo* rade na svojim projektima. (They work a lot on their projects.)

Note: In Serbian, the word "mnogim" can be used as an adjective, pronoun, or adverb, while "mnogo" is an adverb.